   HEB-TEXAS _ LULING, Texas _ Ten percent of the population of
Luling, Texas _ the same turnout as for the city's last mayoral
election _ gathered recently for the same reason: groceries. The
people of Luling came to tell the executives of H-E-B Food Stores
Inc. to replace their tiny, cramped, odoriferous H-E-B _ a former
Piggly Wiggly built more than 40 years ago that is the town's only
food store _ with something bigger and better. (Breyer, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED.
