 &HT;     BILL'S WORLD 
 &HT;     By Bill Tammeus, The Kansas City Star 
 &HT;    
 &HT;    Northern Ireland, says Mr. Clinton, is moving ``from the deep
freeze of despair to the warm sunlight of peace.'' Past the high
wall of cliche.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    ``It's time for us to now go back to the work of the country,''
says the president, ``and give people their government back.'' Who
wants it back?
 &HT;    
