<HEADLINE>
LIST OF PASSENGERS AND CREW KILLED IN SWISSAIR CRASH 
</HEADLINE>
  (See also CRASH-RDP, CRASH-SCENE, CRASH-INQUIRY, CRASH-FAMILIES,
